Smoked Sea Salt and Rosemary Chevre






ADVERTISEMENT
























Smoked Sea Salt and Rosemary Chevre


                Tags:
                
                Dairy and Eggs :: Cheese

Our most versatile flavor. A delicate chèvre hand-blended with smoked sea salt and cracked pepper, marinated in a rosemary-infused extra virgin olive oil blend. An accessible and fresh flavor reminiscent of the Pacific coast.

                    Date product entered market: Nov. 7, 2016
                

ABOUT THE PRODUCER



CHEVOO Inc.
                            Healdsburg, CA
                            707-731-4400


CHEVOO is made from the highest quality goat curd, hand-blended with aromatic spices, herbs, pollens and chilis. It’s then paired with an extra virgin olive oil blend that has been infused with crushed botanicals for 4 – 8 weeks. This combination of flavors in both the chèvre and infused oil makes CHEVOO truly unique.

CHEVOO comes in three distinct varietals. Smoked Sea Salt & Rosemary. California Dill Pollen & Garlic. Aleppo-Urfa Chili & Lemon.

CHEVOO is great with fresh artisanal bread. Or, stirred through steaming pasta. Melted on crusty pizza. Crumbled on garden salads. CHEVOO goes well with … life!





